How to creat a hidden file or folder: 
 mkdir .hiddenfolder       where hiddenfolder is the name of the file or folder you want to hide
 To display it in the CLI:    ls -a
 To creat a multiple directory: mkdir -p  this/is/week1/homework
 How to append a message to a file without a new character: 
 echo "first message" > commandline.txt 
 echo "second message">> commandline.txt
